<p data-start="2948" data-end="3025">Install GPS trackers, sensors, and optionally dash‑cams inside the vehicle.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="3026" data-end="3169">
<p data-start="3029" data-end="3169">Use our <strong data-start="3037" data-end="3075">driver behaviour tracking software</strong> to collect data like vehicle speed, braking force, acceleration, turning, and driver state.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="3170" data-end="3244">
<p data-start="3173" data-end="3244">The system generates easy-to‑read reports and sends real‑time alerts.</p>
</li>
<li data-start="3245" data-end="3355">
<p data-start="3248" data-end="3355">Fleet managers and drivers together review reports, focus training where needed, and adjust driving habits.</p>
</li>
</ol>
